Encapsulation:
Wrapping up the implemetation of the data members(Variables) and methods(Functions) into a single unit to defined in as a Single Class
It is the containing of the data
It is the external implementation of the data

Abtraction:
Hiding the internal Functionality and interfaces the essential and Needed Stuff appropriately
It is the gaining of the data
It is the inbternal implementation of the data(Internal design)
